it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":". Keep this property set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" if","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationView","fragments":[{"kind":"